Date: 1996-07-23

Title: Lukyanov's Screening Operators for the Deformed Virasoro Algebra

Authors: M. Jimbo, M. Lashkevich, T. Miwa and Y. Pugai

Comments: Minor misprints corrected

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. A229 (1997) 285-292

The BRST property of Lukyanov's screening operators in the bosonicrepresentation of the deformed Virasoro algebra is proven.